Package: gak
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 14.0.0)
Description: Global Awesome Keywords - A powerful multi-keyword search tool
 GAK is a command-line tool for searching files with multiple keywords,
 offering flexible context display and advanced filtering options.
 .
 Features include:
  * Multi-keyword searching
  * Recursive directory searching
  * File type filtering
  * Context-aware results
  * Syntax highlighting
  * Binary file filtering
  * And more! 